enter the number of oil packets :3
enter the number of salt packets :6
enter the number of sugar packets :5
enter the number of soap packets :5
enter the number of detergents :2
enter coupon code :9390
customer phone number 7373554744
customer name Sravani
customer address Eluru
tax= 1463.0
bill= 1330
discount 66.5
